metadata.name: The Offering
metadata.description:
Mixed Media. 36"x 20". 150 DPI. 
 To the left, the original drawing was created from the Yellow House Series using India ink on paper created in the style of automatism , photographed and entered into PhotoShop processed into the negative. 
Digital drawings to the right represent the future of the relationship we shall have with Artificial Intelligence between conscious computers and we as human beings.
